  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile, W-SI-01)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package is declared under ProfileMinimal and carries a sha256 content hash but no digital signature, leaving structural integrity unverifiable (W-SI-01). All 13 credibility factors are assessed; seven show achieved levels below required levels and six are flagged as epistemic gaps. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed. Decision: Accepted for synthetic test purposes.",
